message.content: cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR. The paper deals with visual question answering (VQA), which involves image understanding and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is computer vision (cs.CV), followed by computational linguistics (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses machine learning techniques such as attention and memory mechanisms, which fall under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
